sub_title: Senior Specialist, Window Design Operations Tommy Hilfiger Global
summary:
A spatial designer with a multidisciplinary background. I enjoy telling a narrative through memorable experiential design. My current focus is sourcing suppliers, materials and developing strategies that incorporate circularity and sustainability. 
I have developed my design expertise, production and project management abilities through working in fashion, theatrical and commercial interior design projects - from concept to completion, allowing me to bring uniquely creative and efficient ideas to the table.
